//////////////////////////
It's generally easier to think about them as work silos, where sets of commits graduate to a more stable silo when they're fully tested.
//////////////////////////
실험실에서 충분히 테스트하고 실전에 배치하는 과정으로 보면 이해하기 쉽다

[[lrbranch_b]]
